column5: for the longest time, I thought all people were sad as I am. Realized I was just projecting.

I started by decluttering digitally. Lahat ng posts ko sa facebook na memes, I took off from my timeline para yung mga meaningful posts lang ang nakikita pag vinisit yung profile ko (it helps me not to over share meme posts too). I backup my photos on google and delete it from my tablet. For paper files I just throw them away (I don't have a shredder, unfortunately).

*throws self away* 

pero on the serious side, totally ! Anything that doesn't spark you joy should be thrown away.
Ahh fuck. Going through the same thing ☹️
It does feel like that and it hurts. I'm sorry this happened to you too ☹️
Honestly, this is what I wanted to hear 😪 thank you, I will

Rant na sobrang haba sorry 😂 good morning na rin lol. Gusto ko lang ilabas

Ok.....Dahil sa lecheng group work na to, slowly na nawawala na yong 'connection/closeness' na na fe-feel ko sa friends ko 😥 Choose your own group yong proj. 😂

Pag nag tatanong ako noon tungkol sa first proposed product namin, wala man lang silang sagot puro seen. Tas wala man lang silang tulong sa Powerpoint kahit nag aask ako ng help. Kapilitan ginawa ko na lahat haha.

Ako pa yong inaasahang mag explain kasi hindi daw nila alam pero nag provide naman ako ng madaming links about the things we needed to know para ma-defend ng maayos yong product namin. Yung ibang info nga is sinummarize ko na para naman hindi sila mahirapan. Tas pag mag bibigay sila ng idea, hindi nila i-eexplain bakit kelangan yon etc. (Pag tatanongin ko naman sasabihin nalang nila "ay joke lang haha")

Pero in the end, na reject din lang yong unang product namin dahil sa isang feature ng product namin (which is an idea of one of my group mate) kasi hindi niya na defend. Honestly I'm not salty about the idea or the rejection, pero salty ako sa "walang pake" attitude nila 😂

D ko sila pinansin ng ilang days because I was disappointed at them.

Alam kong kasalanan ko rin lang kasi parang tinake-on ko na lahat ng tasks (kasi walang nag vovolunteer/busy daw sila pag nag bigay naman ako ng task), tas ang taas din siguro ng expections ko.

I honestly don't know what to do na because sila yong pinaka close ko sa classroom pero ngayon idk 😅 feel ko kasi ang babaw ko if this is the reason na parang distant na ako sakanila.
